<h2 class="bz-section-title bz-mt-4">BzBento Quick Start</h2>

<DocSection Title="Composition Mode">
    <IconContent>@Icons.BentoGrid</IconContent>
    <ChildContent>
        <p>Build layouts using helper components - no data model needed:</p>
        <CodeBlock Language="razor" Code="@_bentoComposition" />
    </ChildContent>
</DocSection>

<DocSection Title="Helper Components">
    <IconContent>@Icons.Wrench</IconContent>
    <ChildContent>
        <p>BzBento includes specialized components for common UI patterns:</p>
        <ul class="bz-list">
            <li><strong>BzBentoMetric</strong> - KPIs with value, label, and trend indicator</li>
            <li><strong>BzBentoCard</strong> - Image cards with overlay text</li>
            <li><strong>BzBentoFeature</strong> - Feature highlights with icon and description</li>
            <li><strong>BzBentoItem</strong> - Container for custom content (like embedding BzCarousel)</li>
        </ul>
    </ChildContent>
</DocSection>

<DocSection Title="Grid Spanning">
    <IconContent>@Icons.Layout</IconContent>
    <ChildContent>
        <p>Use <code>ColSpan</code> and <code>RowSpan</code> to create varied layouts:</p>
        <CodeBlock Language="razor" Code="@_bentoSpanning" />
